  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "SITE ENGINEER",
  "description": "<p>A site engineer <strong>manages technical aspects of a construction project, ensuring it meets specifications, budget, and schedule by supervising site operations, providing technical advice, and coordinating with various stakeholders</strong>. Key duties include planning, leveling sites, supervising work, checking for compliance with designs and regulations, and managing logistics like materials and manpower.</p>\n<p>Key Responsibilities</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Site Management</strong>:Planning, marking out, and leveling construction sites.</li>\n  <li><strong>Technical Guidance</strong>:Providing technical advice and interpreting contract design documents from architects and clients.</li>\n  <li><strong>Project Coordination</strong>:Overseeing and coordinating site works and manpower, working with project managers, supervisors, architects, and designers.</li>\n  <li><strong>Compliance &amp; Quality</strong>:Ensuring all construction complies with designs, specifications, and relevant regulations.</li>\n  <li><strong>Progress Monitoring</strong>:Reviewing construction schedules, monitoring progress, and reporting delays or issues promptly.</li>\n  <li><strong>Stakeholder Liaison</strong>:Collaborating with various professionals, including construction managers, quantity surveyors, subcontractors, and external vendors.</li>\n  <li><strong>Logistics</strong>:Assisting with material selection, procurement, and logistics planning to keep the project on schedule.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Skills and Requirements</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Technical Knowledge</strong>: Understanding of blueprints, construction methods, and building regulations.</li>\n  <li><strong>Software Proficiency</strong>: Familiarity with project management tools and design software like AutoCAD, MS Project, or Primavera P6.</li>\n  <li><strong>Communication Skills</strong>: Ability to liaise effectively with various professionals and stakeholders.</li>\n  <li><strong>Supervisory Skills</strong>: Experience in supervising contracted staff and managing site operations.</li>\n  <li><strong>Problem-Solving</strong>: Ability to identify and resolve issues that arise during construction.</li>\n</ul>",
  "minimumYearsExperience": 5,
